name: Dark Dissension
Lore: 'The huge Imperial officers corps, with its high rate of turnover, is ripe with competitiveness and ambition. Advancement comes at the expense of another''s career.',
Text: 'USED: Cancel Dark Collaboration or Lone Pilot.LOST: If two Imperials each with ability > 2 are in a battle together, use 2 Force to draw two destiny. Subtract that amount from opponent''s attrition and total power (cannot fall below zero).',
